channel.title: Table Runner on Chrysalis
channel.description: Recent content in Table Runner on Chrysalis

item.title: Black and Red Table Runner
item.description: Table sets with runners have the ideal appearance and feel to spruce up your table top and elevate your occasion. This contemporary coffee table runner also looks great on an entryway table, tv stand, kitchen tables, bedroom dressers, bedroom tables, desk table etc. It can be used as coffee table runner for the centre table,decorative wraps or sashes for chairs, a centre table runner for the living room, a cover for centre table or wood top table etc.
